def: Retired; secluded. "Sequestered scenes." Cowper.Along the cool, sequestered vale of life. Gray.
The quill feathers of the wings of a bird.
One of the orders of Infusoria, characterized by having cilia.In some species the cilia cover the body generally, in others theyform a band around the mouth.
A kind of frock for children.
State or quality of being milky.
A hollow in the side of a hill, where game usually lies. "Fleetfoot on the correi." Sir W. Scott.
A white crystalline substance derived from urethane, used inmedicine as an antipyretic, etc.
Not to be named. [R.] Testament of Love.
A kind of blue sapphire brought from Ceylon. Dana.
